text:
Mr Scott was very professional. When he would b talking about the life ins. & I thought of a ? he took the time 2 listen & answer all the ? pertaining 2 the original ?.
Mr. Jeff was also kind a courteous. He like Mr. Scott, said if I had any problems to call him back which I did. 2 times 1) after I took some time to finagle my original ins. & to see if they would come down on their price. & 2) I had only signed by computer one other time a couple yrs. back & that was with the person there with me walking me through. Mr. Jeff called me back the 1st time but I didn't hear from him about the 2nd. So Mr. Scott received 5 stars but Mr Jeff I subtracted 1.
